        "contenuto_esteso": "(Adnkronos) - BARCELONA, SPAIN - Media OutReach Newswire - 5 March 2026 - Huawei gathered partners, policymakers and international media in Barcelona on March 1 and 2, ahead of Mobile World Congress, to discuss narrowing connectivity and digital skills gaps as artificial intelligence spreads through sectors including healthcare, finance and public services."
